      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. You\u2019ll find it runs smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s the perfect match for someone who wants a dependable, quality car without the 'brand new' price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
